As the pilot increased collective to transition to a hover, the helicopter immediately rolled over 
onto its right side.  The pilot added that the helicopter was positioned into the direct sunlight, 
and he experienced "dazzling sunlight" being reflected from surrounding snow banks.  The 
pilot did not report any mechanical difficulties with the helicopter.
